Let $\hat{{\mathfrak g}}$ be a non-abelian  extension of ${\mathfrak g}$ by ${\mathfrak h}$, and  $\sigma:{\mathfrak g}\rightarrow\widehat{{\mathfrak g}}$ a splitting. Define $\omega:{\mathfrak g}\otimes{\mathfrak g}\rightarrow{\mathfrak h}$,
